          <h1 class="entry-title">Desaru: The Spontaneous Escape</h1>
          <p class="lead">Two adults, two kids, a rented car, and three days across the causeway. What started as a straightforward family getaway turned into a crash course in hotel problem-solving, animal farms, and fruit so fresh you eat it off the cart.</p>

          <div class="featured-image" id="img-001">
